<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no")
    meta(name="description" content="六角西餐廳，切的美味，更對味")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="ie=edge")
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,300i,400,400i,500,500i,700,700i,900,900i', rel='stylesheet')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.5.0/css/all.css', integrity='sha384-B4dIYHKNBt8Bc12p+WXckhzcICo0wtJAoU8YZTY5qE0Id1GSseTk6S+L3BlXeVIU', crossorigin='anonymous')
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="stylesheets/all.css")
    title 六角西餐廳
    link(rel="shortcut icon", type="image/png", href="images/tab_icon.png", sizes="32x32")
  body
    .modal
      button.modal_close(onclick="modalClose()")
        i.fas.fa-times
      .modal_card.transparent
        .modal_main
          .modal_title
            .logo
              img(src="images/logo_l@svg.svg")
            h3 享受美食好味道
          form.login_form
            fieldset.login_field
              legend
                h3 LOGIN
              .input_area.mg_bottom
                label(for="login_account") Email Address*
                .input
                  input#login_account(type="email" placeholder="test@gmail.com" required)
                  span
                    i.far.fa-envelope
              .input_area
                label(for="login_pass") Password*
                .input
                  input#login_pass(type="password" placeholder="Your password" required)
                  span
                    i.fas.fa-unlock-alt
                .forget
                  a(href="#" target="_blank") 忘記密碼?
              .btn.login
                button.signIn(type="submit") 登入
                button.googleIn(type="submit") 以Google帳號登入
            fieldset.register_field(disabled)
              legend
                h3.legend REGISTER
              .input_area.mg_bottom
                label(for="register_account") Email Address*
                .input
                  input#register_account(type="email" placeholder="test@gmail.com" required)
                  span
                    i.far.fa-envelope
              .input_area.mg_bottom
                label(for="register_pass") Password*
                .input
                  input#register_pass(type="password" placeholder="Your password" required)
                  span
                    i.fas.fa-unlock-alt
              .input_area
                label(for="confirm") Confirm*
                .input
                  input#confirm(type="password" placeholder="Confirm your password" required)
                  span
                    i.fas.fa-check-double
              .policy
                |註冊後，即同意 
                a(href="policy.html" target="_blank") 使用條款
                |  和 
                a(href="policy.html" target="_blank") 隱私政策
              .btn.register
                button.signIn(type="submit") 註冊          
        .modal_change
          span 還沒有帳號嗎？
          a(href="javascript:;" onclick="changeModal()") 立即註冊

    .wrap-all#app
      nav
        .topbar
          h1.logo
            a(href="#header") 六角西餐廳
          .top-menu
            ul.hide
              li
                a(href="#features" onclick="tapMenu()") 特色
              li
                a(href="#chef" onclick="tapMenu()") 主廚
              li
                a(href="#reserve" onclick="tapMenu()") 地圖
              li
                a(href="policy.html" onclick="tapMenu()") 使用條款
              li
                button.login_btn(onclick="modalShow()") 登入
          .top-menuToggle-mobile
            button.menu-toggle(onClick="tapMenu()")
              span.icon-bar
              span.icon-bar
              span.icon-bar
      header#header
        .banner
          h2.logo
            img(src="images/logo_w@svg.svg")
          .banner_text
            h2 咬一口就無法忘懷的漢堡
            h3
              |七夕絕對無法錯過的好滋味
              br
              i.fas.fa-utensils
              |六角大漢堡
              i.fas.fa-utensils
      aside.sidebar
        .bubble_list
          ul
            li.purchase
              button(onclick="javascript:window.location.href='cart.html'")
                .cart_icon
                  img(src="images/cart.svg" width="32px" height="32px")
            li.share
              button
                .share_icon
                  img(src="images/share.svg" width="32px" height="32px")
      aside.bottomBar-mobile.if-top
        ul
          li.purchase
            button(onclick="javascript:window.location.href='cart.html'")
              .cart_icon
                img(src="images/cart_w.svg" width="32px" height="32px")
                | 購 物 車
          li.share
            button
              .cart_icon
                img(src="images/share_w.svg" width="32px" height="32px")
                | 分　享

      .wrap
        main.index
          section#features
            h2.title
              |客人總是在詢問
              br
              |這麼好吃的秘訣是什麼
            ul.tips
              li
                img(src="images/feature_1.png")
                h3 台灣本土蔬菜
                p Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Distinctio repudiandae aut molestiae laborum sit! Voluptatibus, consectetur. Dolore suscipit saepe assumenda in velit corrupti provident ducimus!
              li
                img(src="images/feature_2.png")
                h3 專業米其林廚師
                p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Expedita hic asperiores blanditiis. Deserunt soluta eligendi similique rem totam corrupti nihil odio nam inventore voluptas, quae architecto ab eos? Consequatur, cumque.
              li
                img(src="images/feature_3.png")
                h3 對於專業不能退讓
                p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Sequi at dolorem aspernatur iste error cum, omnis quibusdam quam aliquam. Molestiae.
          section#chef
            .chef-img
            .chef_intro
              h2
                |今日主廚：帕金森．梅在帕
                br
