              p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Numquam doloremque exercitationem vel impedit enim corrupti veritatis ipsam eum aliquam repellendus ex in neque fuga sit voluptatem explicabo, molestias modi. Quibusdam laborum assumenda deserunt. Qui illo repellat voluptas nulla cupiditate, quaerat, rem atque velit hic ab necessitatibus, sit officia aperiam modi alias ipsa repellendus quasi nisi minus quisquam similique a eius? Explicabo dolores atque laudantium, porro dignissimos error placeat ea id?
          section#comment
            h2.title 聽聽別人的感想
            ul.criticList
              li(v-for="commentFigure in commentList")
                h3
                  img(:src="'images/' + commentFigure.avatar")
                  span.critic {{commentFigure.critic}}
                p {{commentFigure.comment}}
                h4 {{commentFigure.career}}
          section#reserve
            h2.title
              |我們的位置不太夠坐
              br
              |要不要先訂位呢?
            .reserve_block
              .map_area
              form.form_area
                .info_input
                  label(for="input_name") 姓名
                  input#input_name(type="text" name="Name" placeholder="您的姓名")
                  label(for="input_tel") 電話
                  input#input_tel(type="tel" name="Tel" placeholder="您的手機號碼")
                  label(for="input_mail") 信箱
                  input#input_mail(type="email" name="Mail" placeholder="test@gmail.com")
                  .people_number
                    label(for="input_number") 人數
                    .people_number_input
                      i.fas.fa-minus
                      input#input_number(type="number" step="1" value="1" min="1" max="12")
                      i.fas.fa-plus
                .vege
                  label 是否需要素食
                  .vege_input
                    input#input_no(type="radio" name="Vegetarian" value="yes")
                    label.no(for="input_no") 否
                    input#input_yes(type="radio" name="Vegetarian" value="no")
                    label.yes(for="input_yes") 是
                .form_submit
                  input(type="reset" value="取消")
                  input(type="submit" value="送出")
